list.name: Changes
list.comment:
Implement Generic Library Catalog assignment
- Added generic LibraryItem<T> class with title, author, and itemID attributes - Created GenericCatalog<T> class supporting add, remove, and retrieve operations - Implemented error handling for invalid operations - Built command-line user interface for catalog interactions - Added test scenarios for Books, DVDs, and Magazines - Ensured code readability, modularity, and proper documentation
